Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Mereka masih terjebak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Tsukauchi!\NAll For One meningkatkan kecepatan!
