Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana bantuannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.89,0:01:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.60,0:01:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, tak ada pahlawan\Nyang bisa datang tepat waktu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.89,0:01:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tsukauchi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}All Might!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beginilah seharusnya, Tsukauchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.61,0:01:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, awalnya ini\Nadalah pertarunganku.
