Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Metode bertarung itu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya bisa jika kau memiliki One For All!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Blackwhip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Chargebolt!
