Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu memamerkan kekuatan yang megah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang sibuk melindungi\Nradius tiga meter di wilayah sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku akan memainkan peran itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku tak punya Bakat,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan aku tidak punya peran.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Patah tulang rusuk,\Nmemar di sekujur tubuh.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kelainan pada sistem pernapasan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisakah seseorang menjadi pahlawan\Njika dia tak punya Bakat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dulu, aku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}juga muda sepertimu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah cara
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pria bernama All Might tahu caranya hidup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia jadi lebih muda lagi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Apa dia menyadari itu?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku tidak mau bertanya\Ndan membuatnya sadar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Untuk mengekstrak asam Pinky\Ndari tubuhnya,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}dia memakai Bakat, meski itu membuat\Ndirinya terluka dan rusak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Artinya,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}saat tubuhnya menerima kerusakan,\Nproses Memundurkan Waktu jadi lebih cepat?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan berhenti, Hercules!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Membantu orang lain membuatku senang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ayo lakukan. Kita pasti bisa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Thrusters: Uravity\Ndan Ingenium dengan Kekuatan Penuh.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kelas A, pinjamkanlah kekuatan kalian!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tentacole Perekat Froppy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ini akan meningkatkan mobilitasku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}dan membuat manuverku lebih baik!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Jika tidak, dia akan bosan\Ndengan pertarungan tidak seimbang ini.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Shoto... Tailman...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:28.63,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kukalahkan dia
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dengan jurus selanjutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Jika kerusakan berulang pada tubuh\Nmempercepat Memundurkan Waktu,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}maka akan kugunakan Bakat itu\Nuntuk makin mempercepatnya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:40.60,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Masalahnya adalah sumber energiku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:43.85,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Jika kupakai sesuai manual,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}efeknya tidak akan maksimal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku mengandalkanmu, Anima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mentertawakanku,\Ntapi kau sendiri yang sembunyi dariku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}- Dia di sini.{\i0}\N- Aku tahu rencanamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak akan butuh banyak tenaga
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk mengubah senyum itu\Nmenjadi penderitaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak akan\Nmemakai banyak energi untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Naik!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bohong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menahan kekuatanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senyumanmu telah menghilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, kau hanya tumpukan tulang tua\Nyang tak punya nyali!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau hanya meniru
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kekuatan anak-anak muda itu secara dangkal
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk bertahan hidup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak masalah dengan semua ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini direkam, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang menonton
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}simbol perdamaian mereka\Nberubah jadi simbol tanpa kekuatan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan akan segera musnah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cahaya penuntun mereka akan padam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sungguh tidak mengerti, Temanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang-orang menyala\Ndan padam seperti lampu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski cahayaku padam,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}orang yang menerima cahayaku\Nakan tetap bersinar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan demikian, kegelapan pun diterangi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak perlu cahaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:32.79,tanda,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}NARAPIDANA YANG KABUR DARI TARTARUS,\NPEMBUNUH MASSAL, PENGUMPUL MAYAT, KUNIEDA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sekitar 300 meter di timur laut{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}dari lokasi musuh dibagi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dari 32 pahlawan yang ditugaskan\Nuntuk memusnahkan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}para penjahat yang tersisa,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}hanya satu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}yang masih bisa bergerak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bibitku tumbuh subur hanya dengan daging.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedikit demi sedikit,\Ntanaman ini mulai berakar di dalam diriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku tidak bisa memakai\NBakat Penyerapan Lemak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan menyerah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini adalah bunga terbesar
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang pernah kubuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketika satu bunga mekar,\Nserbuk sari menciptakan reaksi berantai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, tanamannya berkembang biak,\Ndan akarnya menjadi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}perpanjangan anggota tubuhku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak akan kan bisa lari,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dasar pengkhianat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanpa sabuk ini, Laser Pusarmu akan bocor,\Ndan kau tak bisa membidik dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah berusaha keras,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi itu hanya akan\Nmembantu bunga untuk terus tumbuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau hanya ikut-ikutan dan dimanipulasi\Noleh kekuatan yang amat besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:14:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Singkatnya, kehidupanmu memalukan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini, Yuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu ikut senang untukmu, Nak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya aku bilang, "{\i1}Merci{\i0}."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau bilang itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena selalu teringat\Nakan diriku yang memalukan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku dapat berpegang teguh\Npada cahaya mereka yang lebih kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menjadi lebih yakin
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bahwa aku ingin bersinar...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}makin terang!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kau berpegang teguh\Npada sesuatu yang tak terlihat,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau akan mati dengan memalukan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menunggu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pahlawan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:15:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pembelokan Dimensi:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Laser Pusar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang-orang menyala\Ndan padam seperti lampu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:16.58,tanda,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}TATOOIN
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Meski cahayaku padam,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}orang yang menerima cahayaku\Nakan terus bersinar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dengan demikian, kegelapan pun diterangi,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}dan cahaya berkedip lagi di dalam diriku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak merasa akan kalah, All For One!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Koneksi selesai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Energi sedang diisi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Target dikunci.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biarkan nama ini membakarmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:04.84,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak bisa berkelip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Level baterai rendah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kapasitor kelebihan beban.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Fungsi penembakan artileri\Ntidak bisa dipertahankan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan berhenti menembaknya!\NDia akan merangkak ke luar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku akan meniru pertarungan terakhir Star!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meskipun laser pemadatan\Nbukan kemampuanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maka dari itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Getaran Gelombang Suara: Earphone Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku akan lakukan apa pun\Ndengan kekuatanku untuk mengganggu,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}sehingga kau tidak bisa\Nmelarikan diri dari paparan laser.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku mengorbankan Tentacole,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}aku juga menggunakan Thrusters{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}untuk terbang menjauh\Nsaat laser ditembakkan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Baju zirah itu dilapisi\Ndengan resin optik khusus{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}bernama "Gadis Tak Kasatmata"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}yang dapat sedikit mengurangi\Npanas dari laser.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Untuk menciptakan situasi ini, aku tangkis\Nserangan yang kuterima dengan Tailman,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}tapi tubuh bagian bawahku hancur.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kau tidak mengincar kepalaku karena kau\Ningin melihat wajahku kesakitan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:18.91,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Berkat kau, aku bisa lolos dengan mudah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Zirah Berubah Bentuk: Creati!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku tak bisa mengerahkan\Nkekuatan lebih dari ini.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Peluru Pengikat: Grape Juice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Menghilang dan memudarlah...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Selagi sukacita masih menahan derita.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nenek.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa orang kurus yang hitam itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nenek kurang mengerti soal pahlawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang akan terjadi\Njika orang ini menang?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana jika orang ini kalah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini masalah yang menyangkut\Nnegara yang jauh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa pun yang menang,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak ada pengaruhnya terhadap kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Baterai nol persen.\NKapasitor kelebihan beban.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Meledak sekarang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hercules.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kubilang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alat tidak bisa melampaui batasnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia bersinar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar sialan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau lupa tersenyum,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Temanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau amat menyedihkan, All Might.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau kehilangan senyumanmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}harapanmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan kau merangkak di tanah,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}terpelintir oleh keputusasaan\Ndan rasa sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku akan membuatmu hancur\Ndan tak berdaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti yang dulu kau lakukan padaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tubuhku tidak bisa bergerak!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Darah kita
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sama-sama berwarna merah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habisi dia,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}All Might!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menahan penjahat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.18,0:21:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hagakure?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Jangan lihat!\N- Hei...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.87,0:22:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku seharusnya tidak terlihat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.12,0:22:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang sekarat.\NJadi, tak bisa bereaksi dengan benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.08,0:22:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ini belum pernah terjadi,\Nbahkan saat aku menggunakan kekuatan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tunggu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.80,0:22:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tidak, ini pernah terjadi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:24.93,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kau pikirkan
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saat berada di kelas dengan kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.68,0:22:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia sedang sekarat\Ndan melampaui kapasitas biasanya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.14,0:22:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Itu sebabkan gangguan\Npada kemampuan Tidak Terlihatku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.52,0:22:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.56,0:22:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bakatmu jadi makin kuat, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.73,0:22:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang lebih penting,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita harus segera membakar tanaman itu\Ndan menyelamatkan semua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.82,0:22:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti kata Fat,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.79,0:22:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bunga-bunga itu mungkin berhenti tumbuh\Nsetelah tuannya dikalahkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi tidak akan hilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.08,0:22:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hagakure, tolong sesuaikan\Ndan biaskan cahaya
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.38,0:23:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk membakar akar\Nyang telah menggali dagingnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku bisa,\Ntapi apa perutmu akan baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.60,0:23:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah hari terakhirku sebagai murid UA.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.48,0:23:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku rela melakukan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.53,0:23:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pratinjau episode selanjutnya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.03,0:23:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}All Might berada dalam situasi sulit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.74,0:23:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}karena kekuatan All For One\Nyang luar biasa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Yang menyelamatkan dia{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.37,0:23:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}adalah Stain, orang yang dulu\Ndikenal sebagai "Pembunuh Pahlawan".{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.54,0:23:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tapi bukan hanya itu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.25,0:23:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia bukan satu-satunya\Nuluran tangan yang diterima All Might.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.25,0:23:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Episode selanjutnya,\N"Akhir Sebuah Era, dan..."{\i0}
